2018,\u00a0U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng khi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Bangladesh d\u00f9 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Qatar thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f2n t\u00edch l\u0169y ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i mang ra so \u0111\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o U23 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/bxh-bangb-asiad-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2417","checkdouble":"194580"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>Ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal,-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea7y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c v\u00e0 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Nepal t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb,&nbsp;m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 \u1edf Bangladesh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, Olympic Nepal v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014. Nh\u1eefng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Nepal v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u1ea5y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 15/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay c\u1ea3 khi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 tin trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Olympic Nepal. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hai nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3 ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t trong hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u1edf trung t\u00e2m tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1p m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nepal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Nepal \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, NHM Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: 3-0</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan: Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2416","checkdouble":"194581"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi &quot;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin&quot; b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 t\u1ea1i Villas Peros v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 8-0, \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Villas Peros, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u00edn t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CR7 nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ronaldo, tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci hay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Serie A 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. M\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 Marc'Antonio Bentegodi b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi Juventus h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chievo Verona.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2415","checkdouble":"194582"},{"date":"07:48 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-u23-bangladesh-vs-u23-thai-lan-16h00-ngay-168-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan 16h ng\u00e0y 168 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bangladesh-vs-Thai-Lan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Bangladesh vs U23 Th\u00e1i Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>\u00a0</span>U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain: 1-4<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\u1ede b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018,\u00a0U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c minh ch\u1ee9ng khi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua tr\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Bangladesh d\u00f9 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. H\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Qatar thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bangladesh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f2n t\u00edch l\u0169y ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i mang ra so \u0111\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o U23 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/bxh-bangb-asiad-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2414","checkdouble":"194583"},{"date":"08:23 16/08","title":"Diego Costa \"n\u1ed5\" to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Costa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai sau khi gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</h2><h2>Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Costa gi\u00fap Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam qua. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Tallinn l\u00e0 4-2 sau khi hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDiego Costa \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhanh nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 49 gi\u00e2y sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. 26 ph\u00fat sau, Karim Benzema g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ramos \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 71 t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Estonia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Costa \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Atletico v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. V\u00e0 hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Saul Niguez v\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Atletico gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee9 7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Diego Simeone</span>.</div>\r\n<h2>Costa n\u1ed5 to\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Atletico lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tham v\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u nh\u1edd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\">Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2413","checkdouble":"194584"},{"date":"08:29 16/08","title":"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico: Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ed7i nh\u1edb l\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.</h2><h2>\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc Sergio Ramos th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 63, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Los Blancos s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ba n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 mi\u1ec1n k\u00fd \u1ee9c t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u1eadt m\u00ecnh nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n Cristiano Ronaldo n\u1eefa.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-thua-Atletico-Madrid-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergio Ramos t\u1eebng g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1u ph\u00fat sau, Diego Costa \u0111\u01b0a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho Los Blancos. Nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e2ng c\u00fap v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 4 b\u00e0n, nhi\u1ec1u Madridista tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Le Coq Arena (Tallinn, Estonia) \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y ba th\u00e1ng th\u00f4i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang ng\u00e2y ng\u1ea5t men say chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1ec9nh cao xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u. S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh v\u00eanh trong l\u00f2ng n\u1eeda tr\u1eafng th\u00e0nh Madrid th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u &quot;ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn&quot; c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Zizou, hay ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb th\u00eam?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Julen Lopetegui ch\u01b0a kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Zizou sau khi Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 hai. Lopetegui ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0o trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Gareth Bale ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Los Blancos m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Real Madrid hai tay d\u00e2ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng t\u1ef1 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 Los Blancos l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m h\u01a1n, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Zizou l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ch\u00edn n\u0103m, Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o mang v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd 50 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a n\u1eefa, Cristiano Ronaldo gi\u1edd s\u1ebd s\u0103n b\u00e0n cho Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" title=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/kroos-qua-kho-de-thay-the-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Cristiano Ronaldo.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo c\u00f2n m\u1edf l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Marcelo sang Juventus. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea5p l\u1eedng r\u1eb1ng &quot;gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;. Ch\u00ednh Marcelo m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric &quot;ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A&quot; theo l\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. Modric kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Inter Milan. Th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, c\u00f2n ai s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1eefa?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00e9 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico, c\u00f2n Vinicius \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tran tranh Sieu cup chau Au 2018.\" title=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/real-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo. S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Bale c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu khi qu\u00e1 m\u1eabn c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 26 tr\u1eadn, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa ch\u1ec9 19 tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n tr\u00f4i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng th\u00ec giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0... giao h\u1eefu. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4i, Julen Lopetegui nh\u1eadn ra \u00f4ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid-184-194584.html\">Diego Costa n\u1ed5 to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bang-vinh-danh-thibaut-courtois-bi-pha-hoai-180-194580.html\">B\u1ea3ng vinh danh Thibaut Courtois b\u1ecb C\u0110V Atletico Madrid ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\">Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc-172-194531.html\">Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2412","checkdouble":"194585"},{"date":"08:56 16/08","title":"Real thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t, Casemiro v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/casemiro-real-khong-co-gi-de-bao-chua-cho-that-bai-truoc-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Casemiro \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV Lopetegui b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 Real v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><h2>Real thua \u0111\u1eafng Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Atletico Madrid. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 4-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Atletico Madrid v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ch\u1ec9 sau 49 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Costa. Nh\u01b0ng Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u1edbi hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 Ramos. \u0110\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Diego Costa m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Atletico. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Atletico ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1edd th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Saul v\u00e0 Koke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/casemiro-real-khong-co-gi-de-bao-chua-cho-that-bai-truoc-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Bernd Schuster n\u0103m 2007.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Casemiro v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Lopetegui c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 anh \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n. Ronaldo gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang cho Real v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 4 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League trong 5 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Lopetegui. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong> </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2411","checkdouble":"194586"},{"date":"08:57 16/08","title":"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/7/8/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-quyet-gianh-3-diem-dau-tien.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u00e0 Qatar, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Olympic Bangladesh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/24/HLV-Olympic-Thai-Lan-quyet-gianh-3-diem-dau-tien-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Worrawoot Srimaka quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Bangladesh\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay (16/8, gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bangladesh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m qua, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic Bangladesh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh to cao. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, sau khi xem Bangladesh thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Uzbekistan, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1 ra l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bangladesh, Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a Qatar trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. V\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2410","checkdouble":"194587"},{"date":"21:40 15/08","title":"Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua \"b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng\" c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chu-nha-olympic-indonesia-bat-ngo-thua-bai-tuong-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 ba b\u1ea3ng A, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 18 ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi &ldquo;ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda&rdquo; Patriot Chandrabhaga, Indonesia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Milla Luis c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i l\u00ean Palestine, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 18. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u0110\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua 16 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZulfiandi ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Darwish Mohamed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11 m. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Dabbagh Oday \u0111\u00e3 mang ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1ec1 cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Sandouqa Ayman.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic Palestine 1-2 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic Palestine 1-2 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/palestine-indonesia-2120207.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Olympic Indonesia (\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf) thua Olympic Palestine.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Indonesia d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 7 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 V\u1ea1n \u0110\u1ea3o qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Jaya Irfan tho\u00e1t b\u1ea9y b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mamada Rami b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. C\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palestine l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Sandouqa Ayman c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn 45 ph\u00fat kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Trung \u0110\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Darwish Mohamed tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1, n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 51.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng t\u1ef1 \u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Indonesia. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed3n \u00e9p v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-2 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Hong Kong b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan (Trung Qu\u1ed1c) t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi leo l\u00ean ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A. Hai c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Tarres Paramo Jorge (9&rsquo;, 41&rsquo;) v\u00e0 Tan Chun Lok (5&rsquo;, 37&rsquo;) \u0111\u00e3 mang ni\u1ec1m vui cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Kwok Kar Lok Kenneth.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Olympic Palestine t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Trung \u0110\u00f4ng 1 tr\u1eadn, Hong Kong (6 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia (3 \u0111i\u1ec3m) l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t x\u1ebfp c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 ba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y 17/8, trong khi Indonesia ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng L\u00e0o, th\u00ec Hong Kong ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Palestine.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang bang A sau luot tran ngay 15/8.\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng A sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ng\u00e0y 15/8.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/cats.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng A sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ng\u00e0y 15/8.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/ngoi-sao-son-heung-min-du-bi-olympic-han-quoc-van-thang-tennis-o-asiad-2018-472-194561.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn th\u1eafng tennis \u1edf Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-malaysia-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-o-asiad-18-472-194553.html\">Olympic Malaysia kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 \u1edf Asiad 18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong-168-194537.html\">Th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2409","checkdouble":"194562"},{"date":"22:01 15/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/tan-binh-arsenal-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-vo-dich-cua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier League 2018/19 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u00f5 n\u00e9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Man City hay Liverpool, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier League \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/193635-sao-tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Matteo Guendouzi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c bi quan nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n t\u1ef1 tinh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, t\u00e2n binh \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf Emirates v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u00f4i tin Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 xem. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-truoc-mua-giai-201819-su-tro-lai-cua-chu-tu-172-193956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/Arsenal-giu-chan-Ramsey-Vi-chuyen-mon-va-mot-loi-khang-dinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-truoc-mua-giai-201819-su-tro-lai-cua-chu-tu-172-193956.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ch\u00fa T\u01b0</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi, hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi sau 22 n\u0103m th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m d\u1ea7n d\u00e0. Tr\u00e1i ng\u1ecdt th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2408","checkdouble":"194563"},{"date":"22:26 15/08","title":"Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/sao-man-utd-tri-an-mourinho-sau-khi-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce quy k\u1ebft b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thua-cua-arsenal-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 dung th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng pressing xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 y nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Arsenal tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2 reo khi Petr Cech quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sang ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9. Khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Man City r\u1ed3i anh mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec th\u00ec l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2407","checkdouble":"194564"},{"date":"23:00 15/08","title":"Sao Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/sao-arsenal-tu-sanh-minh-voi-ronaldo-va-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cGia nh\u1eadp Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho t\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec trong s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u x\u00e1n l\u1ea1n cho t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/aubameyang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, c\u00e1i \u201ckh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Gabon c\u1ee7a Dortmund n\u00f3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi nhanh nh\u01b0 ch\u1edbp, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi anh ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea5y Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i thu th\u1eadp s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Salah \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y r\u1ea5t nhanh r\u1ed3i c\u01a1 m\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch xem nh\u1eefng b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh ghi l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cN\u0103m nay trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 37km/h v\u00e0 ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Mbappe \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 29, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/3/goc-arsenal-thanh-hinh-voi-aubameyang-va-nhung-van-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Aubameyang v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon, nh\u01b0ng song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi bi\u1ebft bao h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2406","checkdouble":"194565"},{"date":"23:39 15/08","title":"Man Utd \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/man-utd-don-day-du-trong-phao-tro-lai-cuoi-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u00eam hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p hai v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t v\u00f4 duy\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jesse Lingard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Pogba, Rashford v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, Lukaku, Lingard v\u00e0 Fellaini c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2405","checkdouble":"194567"}]}